Prioritizing hygiene, masking, and self-isolation when symptomatic are crucial, alongside bolstering immunity through healthy lifestyle choices to navigate this evolving health situation effectively.

description: Mumbai experienced a historic monsoon onset on May 26, 2025, the earliest ever recorded, prompting a red alert for Mumbai, Thane, and Raigad. Waterlogging and tree falls were reported across the city, with authorities responding to road disruptions.

author: TOI NEWS DESK
description: India reports a rise in active Covid-19 cases, exceeding 1,000, with 752 recent confirmations, according to the Union health ministry. The nationwide discharge tally is 4,45,11,545, with 5,33,673 fatalities recorded. Kerala leads with 430 active cases, followed by Maharashtra, Delhi and Karnataka. Several states, including Andaman and Nicobar, currently report no active cases.

Police arrested two men, Hari Palvi and Sunil Korku, accused of torturing her and damaging her private parts. description: President Trump defended his tariff strategy, prioritizing military and high-tech manufacturing over industries like textiles, despite criticism from apparel and footwear associations concerned about increased costs for consumers. Trump also extended the deadline for imposing tariffs on EU goods to allow for further negotiations.

description: The Indian Air Force commemorated 'Operation Safed Sagar', its air campaign during the 1999 Kargil War, supporting Operation Vijay to evict Pakistani troops from Indian positions along the LoC.
